  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Existing law provides various sources of funding for water and transportation projects.\n\nThis bill would appropriate $455,500,000 from the General Fund to the San Luis and Delta-Mendota Water Authority for the purpose of funding the State Highway 152 Route improvements required to complete the B.F. Sisk Dam Raise and Reservoir Expansion Project."
    }
  ],
